name: Syntric Rubber Products
overview: Established in the year 1979, at Pune (Maharashtra, India), we, “Syntric Rubber Products”, are known as the most reputed manufacturer and supplier of qualitative assortment of Industrial Products such as Metal Bonded Parts, V Seals, Pneumatic Seals, Mountings and O Rings. These products are manufactured using high grade raw material and sophisticated technology. The offered range is designed with high precision in order to meet the international quality standards. Apart from this, the offered products are highly appreciated among clients for their hassle free operation, smooth functioning, sturdy construction, dimensional accuracy and high durability. Our quality controllers rigorously examine these products on various parameters to ensure flawlessness and defect free assortment. Furthermore, we offer our products in various specifications and in customized form too as per the precise requirements of clients at most economical price range.
